<h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0; font-size:22px; font-weight:600;">
    ⚠️ Document Requires Resubmission
</h2>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0;">
    Hello {{homeBuyerName}},
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Your document submission requires attention. Please review the details below and resubmit as needed.
</p>

<table style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:20px 0; border-collapse:collapse;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Document:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;"><strong>{{documentName}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Step:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{stepName}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{#if contractNumber}}
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Contract:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{contractNumber}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if propertyName}}
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:5px 20px 5px 0; color:#666;">Property:</td>
        <td style="padding:5px 0;">{{propertyName}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
</table>

<div style="background-color:#FFF8E1; border-left:4px solid #FFC107; padding:15px; margin:20px 0;">
    <p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:0;">
        <strong>Reason:</strong><br/>
        {{reason}}
    </p>
</div>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    <strong>What to do next:</strong>
</p>
<ol style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0; padding-left:20px;">
    <li>Review the reason provided above</li>
    <li>Prepare the correct document</li>
    <li>Log in to your dashboard and resubmit</li>
</ol>

<a href="{{dashboardLink}}"
   style="display:inline-block; background-color:#19C2AB; color:#ffffff; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none; padding:12px 25px; border-radius:5px; margin:20px 0;">
    Resubmit Document
</a>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:25px 0 10px 0;">
    If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.
</p>

<p style="font-size:14px; line-height:22px; margin:10px 0;">
    Best regards,<br/>
    The QShelter Team
</p>
